// Page HeroOrVigilante Text :
"P663769585" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Doc Quantum's Moral Quandary</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've been contacted by the notorious Doc Quantum, he presents you with a curious situation.<br><br><color orange>'Salutations {HeroName},<br><br>Please excuse my intrusion, I am sure you are very busy with...whatever...it is that you do.  What I am interested in is why you do it.  So, you're going to be a volunteer in an experiment of mine.  I've arranged an interesting scenario for you.  A notorious Rogue Isles' villain Hollow Point and his so-called militia have subdued, unmasked and neutralized the powers of a few of Paragon City's more patriotic heroes and have orders to execute them in 1 hour.  However, I have just heard word that Hollow Point himself, ever the busy man, has set out on his next scheme to take over a local newspaper to publish anti-government propaganda. What will do you {HeroName}?<br><br>Will you save those careless heroes who managed to get themselves captured, and let that <i>insane</i> terrorist Hollow Point go free?<br><br>Or will you stop the cause of all this, Hollow Point and let those patriotic defenders of Paragon City die?<br><br>This should be an interesting experiment, thank you for your cooperation.'</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1150478882" "HERO: Rescue the subdued heroes."
// Answer Text :
"P538097482" "VIGILANTE: Take out Hollow Point."
// Page Rogue Text :
"P2817669130" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Doc Quantum's Moral Quandary</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You've been contacted by the notorious Doc Quantum, he presents you with a curious situation.<br><br><color orange>'Salutations {HeroName},<br><br>Please excuse my intrusion, I am sure you are very busy with...whatever...it is that you do.  What I am interested in is why you do it.  So, you're going to be a volunteer in an experiment of mine.  I've arranged an interesting scenario for you.  A notorious Rogue Isles' villain Hollow Point and his so-called militia have subdued, unmasked and neutralized the powers of a few of Paragon City's more patriotic heroes and have orders to execute them in 1 hour.  However, I have just heard word that Hollow Point himself, ever the busy man, has set out on his next scheme to take over a local newspaper to publish anti-government propaganda. What will do you {HeroName}?</color><br><br>You're familiar with Hollow Point and know he and his men won't hesitate to kill these heroes.  You could give them a hand and get them out of that grim situation."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


