// Page HeroOrVigilante Text :
"P3094396019" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Malta Gunslinger Action Figure</color></span></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span></scale><br><br>You find what appears to be an...action figure of a Malta Gunslinger? Who in their right mind would make this? You tinker around with it a bit, noticing it has a switch on the back. You flick it a few times, noticing the arm chopping up and down. You then see a small piece of paper sticking out from beneath the arm. You pull it out, reading over the secret message...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Bravo 9 - <br><br>We have a traitor. Black Panther 952 has defected to Longbow. This happened at 2100 last night. Proceed with phase one of recovery. Retrieve Black Panther 952 and deliver to warehouse for mind wipe.<br><br> - Director 4</color></scale></font><br><br>It seems that a higher up agent in Malta has defected - luckily you were able to intercept this message, straight from one of the mysterious Malta Directors. You doubt, however, that this was the only one sent. Knowing Malta, they already have a recovery team on the way to attack that Longbow base where Black Panther 952 is being held. If something isn't done soon, that base will be overwhelmed and Black Panther will be taken back by Malta!<br><br>Although...this Malta agent has probably put away a good amount of heroes. Who is he to deserve <i>any</i> mercy in this situation? Did he show mercy to the heroes who begged him for it? No. He doesn't belong in the hands of Longbow or Malta - he deserves to face justice. <i>Your</i> justice."
// Answer Text :
"P3576447244" "HERO: Save Black Panther 952!"
// Answer Text :
"P1413633392" "VIGILANTE: Put down Black Panther 952!"
// Page Rogue Text :
"P748820547" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Malta Gunslinger Action Figure</color></span></font><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span></scale><br><br>You find what appears to be an...action figure of a Malta Gunslinger? Who in their right mind would make this? You tinker around with it a bit, noticing it has a switch on the back. You flick it a few times, noticing the arm chopping up and down. You then see a small piece of paper sticking out from beneath the arm. You pull it out, reading over the secret message...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Bravo 9 - <br><br>We have a traitor. Black Panther 952 has defected to Longbow. This happened at 2100 last night. Proceed with phase one of recovery. Retrieve Black Panther 952 and deliver to warehouse for mind wipe.<br><br> - Director 4</color></scale></font><br><br>This was certaintly a creative way to find out about this Malta plot. They're an organization that knows only one thing - the destruction of all super powered beings. Which makes it <i>awfully</i> hard to do any business with them. You've heard of many situations of other...'business dealers' finding out the hard way that Malta doesn't deliver on their bargains. Maybe it's time for someone to help put Malta in their place - if Longbow gets to keep Black Panther 952, it could mean a lot of Malta's secrets are revealed. That could be a help to everyone against the common enemy of Malta."
// Page UnableToInvestigate Text :
// Answer Text :
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


